data.text:
This form is for use by University of Waterloo graduate students who are registered in the joint Waterloo/Laurier Geography program and who are enrolling for geography courses taught at Wilfrid Laurier University. Completion of this form is required in order to be provided with access to WLU's student learning space.

This request will be forwarded to WLU for approval and processing each week.
